// "Hosted on Filecoin Onchain Cloud" badge — shared across every site in the monorepo.
---

<div class="foc-badge">
  <a href="https://filecoin.cloud" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <span>Hosted on</span>
    <img src="/img/foc-logo-light.svg" alt="Filecoin Onchain Cloud" loading="lazy" />
  </a>
</div>

<style>
  .foc-badge {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 0 1rem;
